data.name: labelInfo.Text
data.value: In this window, you can change the locality used in the Planetary Hours Calendar. These changes are temporary, and the next time you open the Calendar the default location will be used. To permanently change your locality, click the "Change settings" link in the Calendar window. Changes made in the Locality window have no effect on the glyph icon displayed in the system tray.
